Learn More About Us and How We Can Help You
Starke Lake Studios is a family owned, multi-platinum commercial recording studio. We are located in the greater Orlando, Florida area, right next to the beautiful Starke Lake in Ocoee, FL. We have been around since 1982 and have had the pleasure of working on a large variety of projects. Check out some of our clients down below!
We strive to provide top quality service in a creative and serene atmosphere that helps our clients feel at home. Whether you are looking to record your next big hit, mix and/or master a song you already have, rehearse for an upcoming show, or record a music video, let Starke Lake Studios be your next destination.
